data.description: Home, sweet home! Check out this charming 3-bed, 2-bath property in Glennwilde! Offering a 2-car garage and a cozy porch to sit & enjoy the peaceful neighborhood. Welcoming interior features tile flooring complemented by soothing palette. The bright living and dining rooms merge seamlessly, making it an ideal spot for relaxing and gatherings. Cook your favorite meals in this impeccable kitchen boasting wood cabinets, SS appliances, granite counters, a pantry, and sliding glass doors leading to the back patio. Have a good night's sleep in this cozy main suite showcasing a walk-in closet & a private bathroom for convenience. Designed for al fresco dining, the lovely backyard provides a covered patio, pavers, and a fire pit to gather around during chilly evenings. Make this gem yours!
